        <div class="projectSummary">Developed a C#/.NET 8 mobile app feature enabling customers to pre-arrange service loaner vehicles before automotive appointments. Integrated a third-party API and internal databases to streamline the process. Utilized Azure DevOps for version control and worked in Visual Studio and VS Code environments.</div>
    </div>
