        <div class="projectSummary">Established a CI/CD pipeline integrating Visual Studio, Azure DevOps, and Google Cloud Platform to support modern deployment practices. Currently leading the migration of the legacy .NET Framework 4.8 application to .NET 8, including project file upgrades, library updates, and code refactoring.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="obj">
        <h4 class="projectTitle">Extended Warranty</h4>
        <div class="projectSummary">Built a mobile app feature enabling users to purchase extended vehicle warranties end-to-end. Integrated four third-party APIs to verify vehicle details, retrieve contract options, generate contracts, handle digital signatures, and process payments. Streamlined the entire contracting workflow within a single user experience.</div>
    </div>

